Steps

    - set up express/modules needed
    - set up routes for resources
    - build schemas and models for our DB
    - link those models to our routes
    - add rendering to our routes, or add requests from our front end for the data
    - incorporate and error class / error handling (DONT SKIP)
    - incorporate data/schema/form validation
    - authentication & authorization
    - find hosting service
    - install node,npm, and all dependencies
    - install pm2 to handle running and restarting processes while away from remote machine
    - deploy app using hosting service